    "serialOutput": [],
    "sketchCode": "// Starfish LED Circuit — All Arms Blink Together\n// 5 arms: Top, Top-Right, Bottom-Right, Bottom-Left, Top-Left\nint pins[] = {9, 10, 11, 12, 13};\n\nvoid setup() {\n  for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {\n    pinMode(pins[i], OUTPUT);\n  }\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  // All 5 arms ON\n  for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) digitalWrite(pins[i], HIGH);\n  delay(500);\n\n  // All 5 arms OFF\n  for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) digitalWrite(pins[i], LOW);\n  delay(500);\n}\n",
